Good news! We heard what you had to say and have been working hard to improve our app. The new version is finally ready to go! We hope you'll love the new check-in process, which is easier to use and more intuitive than ever. We also updated the login page and made it super-sleek. So go ahead, update your Gympass app and we promise that you'll have a much better experience!

P.S. If you have a minute, please comment down below. We'd love to hear what you think!

Enjoy!
